:: TanPhoneSelfie [event phoneselfie noevents nobr]
<<if $phoneselfieconvoactive>>
    <<egoto TanPhoneMenu>>
<<elseif $phoneselfieactive and $phoneselfiesent>>
    <<run setup.Tanning.begin_tan_phone_selfie_convo($phoneselfiesent, $phoneselfietarget or $tanphoneselfietarget)>>
    <<egoto TanPhoneMenu>>
<<else>>
    <<egoto TanPhoneMenu>>
<</if>>